<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Sami Dolphin Online Audio Visual Advertising and Promotion</title>
  <style>
    body { margin:0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height:1.6; background:#fdfdfd; color:#333; }
    header { background:#0d47a1; color:#fff; padding:1rem 2rem; position:sticky; top:0; z-index:1000; }
    header h1 { margin:0; font-size:1.5rem; }
    nav { margin-top:0.5rem; }
    nav a { color:#fff; margin-right:1rem; text-decoration:none; font-weight:bold; }
    nav a:hover { text-decoration:underline; }

    .hero { background:linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.5), rgba(0,0,0,0.5)), url('https://picsum.photos/1600/800?grayscale'); background-size:cover; color:#fff; text-align:center; padding:6rem 2rem; }
    .hero h2 { font-size:2.5rem; margin-bottom:1rem; }
    .hero p { font-size:1.2rem; }

    section { padding:3rem 2rem; max-width:1000px; margin:auto; }
    section h2 { text-align:center; margin-bottom:2rem; color:#0d47a1; }
    .services { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr)); gap:1.5rem; }
    .card { background:#fff; border-radius:10px; padding:1.5rem; box-shadow:0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); transition:transform .2s; }
    .card:hover { transform:translateY(-5px); }

    footer { background:#0d47a1; color:#fff; text-align:center; padding:1rem; margin-top:2rem; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Sami Dolphin</h1>
    <nav>
      <a href="#home">Home</a>
      <a href="#about">About</a>
      <a href="#services">Services</a>
      <a href="#blog">Blog</a>
      <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section class="hero" id="home">
    <h2>Innovative Audio-Visual Advertising & Promotion</h2>
    <p>Helping brands stand out with creative, impactful campaigns.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="about">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>Welcome to your one-stop destination for innovative online audio-visual advertising and promotion. We specialize in creating engaging video and audio content that helps brands stand out, connect with their audience, and drive real results.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="services">
    <h2>Our Services</h2>
    <div class="services">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Video Commercials</h3>
        <p>Dynamic and creative video ads designed to capture attention.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Audio Promotions</h3>
        <p>Professional audio spots to boost your brand identity.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Campaign Strategy</h3>
        <p>Tailored advertising campaigns to meet your business goals.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="blog">
    <h2>Blog</h2>
    <p>Coming soon: articles and updates on creative advertising, promotion tips, and our latest projects.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="contact">
    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>Email: <a href="mailto:yourname@example.com">yourname@example.com</a></p>
    <p>Or use our contact form (coming soon!).</p>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 Sami Dolphin Online Audio Visual Advertising and Promotion | Created by Samson Tesfaye</p>
  </footer>
</body>
